('13872277-ad30-4ca9-b39a-d2a434dcc49b', 'a16817d6-ff58-424a-8b41-d38710f002ea', 'Issue #6: Claude/review project m vnwt\nState: closed\nLabels:\n\n## Summary by Sourcery\n\nIntegrate the frontend with new and existing backend APIs for circles, goals, cards, notifications, payments, and support, replacing demo data and local-only state updates with persisted server-driven data flows.\n\nNew Features:\n- Add backend-powered circle chat, membership management, and join/create flows that load and persist data via circlesService.\n- Introduce goal contribution, withdrawal, and deletion capabilities wired to backend goalsService with a reusable contribution modal.\n- Implement virtual card top-up and freeze/unfreeze actions backed by cardService with real balance retrieval.\n- Add full CRUD support for payment methods using a dedicated paymentMethodsService.\n- Introduce paymentsService and supportService to handle contributions and support tickets via backend APIs.\n- Add notificationsService to synchronize notification read state with the server and fetch real notifications.\n- Expose global loading, error, and refreshData handling in AppContext tied to authenticated user data fetching.', 0, 'tauri', '2026-05-25 00:43:20'),
('13e61e65-a704-41ef-8f98-d23ae99eb573', 'edb653b9-dff9-488f-86d9-00501125c895', 'PR #8: Claude/review project m vnwt\nState: closed\nLabels: \n\n## Summary by Sourcery\n\nImplement full goal management API for authenticated users and adjust a wallet icon usage in the Circles page.\n\nNew Features:\n- Add CRUD, contribution, withdrawal, progress, and savings program enrollment endpoints for user goals in the API.\n\nEnhancements:\n- Expose predefined savings programs and computed goal metrics through the goals API.\n- Standardize wallet icon usage on the Circles page by switching to the shared WalletIcon component.', 0, 'tauri', '2026-05-25 00:43:20'),
