('20cb7c81-6c29-443e-8b41-881fbdae42ef', 'c0542233-68da-4032-aebb-d6f34263e360', '(30) → Dashboard, Orders, Products, Delivery, Shops...\n    ├── driver/   (15) → Dashboard, Delivery, Navigation, Wallet, Zones...\n    └── common/   (5)  → Settings, Help, About, Terms, Privacy\n```\n\n\n\n## 🔌 Guide intégration API\n\nChaque fichier `src/data/*.js` → remplacer par appel API :\n\n| Mock file | API endpoint | Méthodes |\n|---|---|---|\n| products.js | `/api/products` | GET POST PUT DELETE |\n| vendors.js | `/api/vendors` | GET |\n| categories.js | `/api/categories` | GET |\n| reviews.js | `/api/products/:id/reviews` | GET POST |\n| vendorData.js | `/api/vendor/*` | GET POST PUT |\n| driverData.js | `/api/driver/*` | GET POST PUT |\n\n### Pattern API recommandé\n```jsx\n// Créer: src/services/api.js\nimport axios from \'axios\';\nexport const api = axios.create({ baseURL: \'https://api.lamuka.cg\' });\n\n// Dans un écran:\nimport { api } from \"../../services/api\";\nconst [products, setProducts] = useState([]);\nuseEffect(() => { api.get(\'/products\').then(r => setProducts(r.data)) }, []);\n```', 2, 'tauri', '2026-05-25 00:43:20'),
('2276e859-19a3-45ce-82ce-2272f4a1414b', 'dfd3c9ba-fb7a-4582-be79-5747bb7ea89e', 'PR #2: Claude/review chatbot 1 i2q3\nState: closed\nLabels: \n\n## Summary by Sourcery\n\nRevamp the NovAI chat and auth interfaces with a new visual design and UX improvements, including enhanced message rendering and onboarding.\n\nNew Features:\n- Add quick-start suggestion cards on the welcome screen that prefill and submit example prompts.\n- Introduce code block headers with language labels and copy-to-clipboard controls in assistant messages.\n- Enable textarea-based message input with auto-resize and Enter-to-send behavior.\n- Add mobile sidebar overlay behavior and improved sidebar toggling for small screens.\n\nEnhancements:\n- Refresh the global color palette, typography, and component styles for a more modern, compact UI across chat, sidebar, and auth pages.\n- Redesign the chat layout, message styling, and header actions to better support long-form conversations and code snippets.\n- Rebuild the auth page with a two-panel branding layout, improved form fields, and clearer call-to-action copy.\n- Update avatars and branding to use a consistent NovAI identity, including new SVG icons for the app and assistant.\n- Improve markdown rendering for tables and code blocks, including updated spacing and highlighting styles.\n\nChores:\n- Refine the Ollama connection error message to provide clearer startup instructions for users.', 0, 'tauri', '2026-05-25 00:43:20'),
('22bfa600-363f-4032-b935-59713b3d9216', '1ade2a1a-8fe6-4231-9efa-0fd92022e0af', 'PR #2: delete directory\nState: closed\nLabels: \n\n## Summary by Sourcery\n\nChores:\n- Delete the .claude/settings.local.json configuration file from the project.', 0, 'tauri', '2026-05-25 00:43:19'),
('22de1bcc-ab84-4844-a933-df2cc9c0f31d', '207d596f-8788-4112-8111-6aec09070d30', '# 🏪 Lamuka Market\n\n> Multi-commerce marketplace for Congo 🇨🇬 — **88 composants | 35+ écrans | 3 modes**  \n> Built by **Lamuka Tech** — Brazzaville\n\n## 🚀 Quick Start\n\n```bash\nnpm install\nnpm run dev     # → http://localhost:3000\nnpm run build   # → /dist\n```\n\n## 📂 Architecture (108 fichiers source)\n\n```\nsrc/\n├── App.jsx                      # Router principal + state global\n├── main.jsx                     # Entry point\n├── data/                        # 🗃️ Mock data (→ remplacer par API)\n│   ├── products.js              # 14 articles\n│   ├── vendors.js               # 8 commerçants\n│   ├── categories.js            # 10 catégories\n│   ├── reviews.js / coupons.js / notifications.js / addresses.js / chats.js\n│   ├── vendorData.js            # V_ORDERS, V_PRODUCTS, V_WALLET, V_STATS...\n│   └── driverData.js            # D_DELIVERIES, D_HISTORY, D_STATS...\n├── utils/helpers.js             # fmt() disc()\n├── styles/global.js             # CSS complet (520 lignes)\n└── screens/\n    ├── auth/     (5)  → Splash, Onboarding, Login, OTP, ProfileCompletion\n    ├── buyer/    (27) → Home, Search, Detail, Cart, Checkout, Reviews...\n    ├── vendor/   (30) → Dashboard, Orders, Products, Delivery, Shops...\n    ├── driver/   (15) → Dashboard, Delivery, Navigation, Wallet, Zones...\n    └── common/   (5)  → Settings, Help, About, Terms, Privacy\n```\n\n## 🔌 Guide intégration API\n\nChaque fichier `src/data/*.js` → remplacer par appel API :\n\n| Mock file | API endpoint | Méthodes |\n|---|---|---|\n| produc', 0, 'tauri', '2026-05-25 00:43:19'),
