('2df7b6ea-fc72-43ed-b61c-4dbf3a4fd0f7', '22a27ed1-ad7e-4761-b823-2a6b433ee933', 'PR #2: delete directory\nState: closed\nLabels: \n\n## Summary by Sourcery\n\nChores:\n- Delete the .claude/settings.local.json configuration file from the project.', 0, 'tauri', '2026-05-25 00:43:19'),
('2ef19b09-5d46-49a1-9e61-73575aa683da', 'd0af8ff8-3026-4367-bdf7-97b039517b24', 'Issue #7: Claude/review project m vnwt\nState: closed\nLabels:\n\n## Summary by Sourcery\n\nImplement final optional features and onboarding experience across circles, goals, wallet, auth, profile, and documentation to complete the app feature set.\n\nNew Features:\n- Add public circle discovery screen with search and the ability to join public circles from the backend.\n- Introduce payout slot selection backed by live slot data with fallback demo slots.\n- Add identity verification flow with national ID upload simulation before completing circle registration.\n- Implement splash and multi-step onboarding screens with persisted completion state and initial routing logic.\n- Provide edit modals for circles and savings goals to update key details via backend services.\n- Enable wallet balance display (card vs wallet) along with transaction filtering by type and date range, plus a payment confirmation modal for contributions.\n- Redesign login and registration screens with new gradient headers and improved form layouts.\n- Add security logs filtering UI by activity type and time period, wired to a new security service placeholder.', 0, 'tauri', '2026-05-25 00:43:20'),
('2f1705b3-49cf-446a-ad24-b46ef75a39f2', 'bbf5c610-6214-4659-b0d6-5f2b9be91d63', 'Issue #1: Refactor: Complete architectural overhaul of Kolo Tontine frontend\nState: closed\nLabels: \n\nThis commit represents a comprehensive refactoring of the entire frontend codebase, transforming a monolithic 11,254-line App.tsx file into a maintainable, scalable, and modern React application.\r\n\r\n## Major Changes:\r\n\r\n### Architecture & Structure\r\n- Created proper folder structure (components, pages, hooks, services, etc.)\r\n- Implemented clean component architecture with separation of concerns\r\n- Reduced main App.tsx from 11,254 lines to 13 lines\r\n- Backed up original App.tsx as App.tsx.backup for reference\r\n\r\n### Routing & Navigation\r\n- Installed and configured React Router DOM\r\n- Implemented protected routes with authentication guards\r\n- Created route-based navigation system\r\n- Added bottom navigation component\r\n\r\n### State Management\r\n- Created AuthContext for global authentication state\r\n- Implemented useAuth hook for easy auth state access\r\n- Set up proper context providers\r\n\r\n### TypeScript & Type Safety\r\n- Created comprehensive TypeScript types for all entities\r\n- Added proper type definitions (User, LikeLemba, Goal, Transaction, etc.)\r\n- Configured Vite environment types\r\n\r\n### Internationalization\r\n- Installed and configured react-i18next\r\n- Extracted all translations from hardcoded strings\r\n- Created separate translation files (en.json, fr.json)\r\n- Implemented proper i18n configuration\r\n\r\n### API Layer\r\n- Created abstraction layer for all API calls\r\n- Implemented A', 0, 'tauri', '2026-05-25 00:43:20'),
