('3bfe4fe8-f5a6-4e7f-b2a5-6c63ac5ba8d2', '0f0d80da-5ec2-466b-937f-07daf18b9811', 'Issue #1: Firebase cloud messaging integration\nState: closed\nLabels: \n\n## Summary by Sourcery\n\nSwitch customer booking push notifications from OneSignal to Firebase Cloud Messaging and tidy related controller code.\n\nNew Features:\n- Send booking confirmation push notifications to customers via Firebase Cloud Messaging.\n\nEnhancements:\n- Simplify and reformat reservation booking controller logic and notification payload construction for readability.', 0, 'tauri', '2026-05-25 00:43:19'),
