('48a176e4-dcd0-4aaa-adc2-084439634749', '3b97434d-049c-4d32-ab6e-cabf982b7ffe', 'migration\r\n\r\n### Security\r\n- Comprehensive security review documented in SECURITY_REVIEW.md\r\n- Identified critical vulnerabilities in auth and payment flows\r\n- Documented recommendations for secure implementation\r\n- Created security checklist for production readiness\r\n\r\n### Documentation\r\n- Created REFACTORING_GUIDE.md with complete migration guide\r\n- Documented new architecture and folder structure\r\n- Added examples and best practices\r\n- Created development workflow guidelines\r\n- Added .env.example for environment configuration\r\n\r\n### Testing & Build\r\n- Fixed TypeScript compilation errors\r\n- Successfully built production bundle\r\n- Verified all imports and dependencies\r\n\r\n## Files Added:\r\n- src/components/ui/* (Button, Input, Card, Badge, Modal)\r\n- src/components/layout/* (Header, BottomNavigation)\r\n- src/pages/* (Home, Circles, Wallet, Card, Profile)\r\n- src/context/AuthContext.tsx\r\n- src/services/* (api, auth, circles, goals, transactions)\r\n- src/types/index.ts\r\n- src/i18n/* (config, en.json, fr.json)\r\n- src/routes/index.tsx\r\n- src/vite-env.d.ts\r\n- SECURITY_REVIEW.md\r\n- REFACTORING_GUIDE.md\r\n- .env.example\r\n\r\n## Dependencies Added:\r\n- react-router-dom: ^6.x\r\n- react-i18next: ^14.x\r\n- i18next: ^23.x\r\n\r\n## Migration Status:\r\n✅ Core architecture complete\r\n✅ Type system established\r\n✅ API layer ready\r\n✅ Basic pages created\r\n🚧 Screen migration from old App.tsx in progress\r\n\r\n## Next Steps:\r\n- Migrate remaining screens from App.tsx.backup\r\n- Implement authentication flow\r\n- Add form validation\r\n- Implement error boundaries\r\n- Add loading states and notifications\r\n- Write tests\r\n\r\nhttps://claude.ai/code/session_01DQYEizP5oC7ge3u6Uq7Tpu', 3, 'tauri', '2026-05-25 00:43:19'),
('4a160cdd-9c1a-4f90-9a7b-86f5b8c222d9', '602069fc-0856-4156-ba6c-542648cc982e', 'ar cercle, Assistant IA \"Lamu\"\n- Objectifs de groupe, Partage de frais (split bills)\n- Parrainage avec code + bonus 5000 FCFA\n\n### Autres\n- Porte-monnaie familial, Micro-assurance (3 plans)\n- Éducation financière (cours + tips), Mode sombre (preview)\n- Notifications, Paramètres, Export PDF/CSV, Dispute/Médiation\n\n## 🏗 Structure\n\n```\nsrc/\n├── App.jsx          # Application complète (router + tous les écrans)\n├── theme.js         # Couleurs, constantes\n├── icons.jsx        # Icônes SVG + SvgIc component\n├── data.js          # Données mock (membres, cercles, transactions...)\n├── main.jsx         # Point d\'entrée\n└── index.css        # Styles globaux\n```\n\n## 🎨 Design\n- Palette : Navy (#0B1D3A) + Gold (#F5A623) + Blue (#1A56DB)\n- Style Money Fellows adapté pour le Congo\n- Icônes SVG (pas d\'emojis)\n- Responsive : plein écran mobile, cadre téléphone desktop\n\n## 🛠 Stack\n- React 18 + Vite\n- Single-file architecture (pas de dépendances UI)\n- Prêt pour découpage en modules\n\n## 📞 Contact\n- Lamuka Tech · Brazzaville, Congo\n- business@lamuka-tech.com\n- +242 06 466 3469\n\n© 2026 Lamuka Tech. Tous droits réservés.', 1, 'tauri', '2026-05-25 00:43:19'),
('4ca2a86c-8c3e-4471-9772-fc27eb18b127', '73ac3f67-6982-431e-aef6-117097e9c846', 'PR #1: test commit\nState: closed\nLabels: \n\n## Summary by Sourcery\n\nDocumentation:\n- Add a suivi.md document describing how to install all dependencies with yarn.', 0, 'tauri', '2026-05-25 00:43:19'),
('4d67bdd8-f44a-41cd-bf0d-227fc2eff98b', '1fad8e26-03f9-4368-a2c1-b6e4b9e27c0b', '## Key features\n\n- **Admin panel** (rose theme) — full platform management: builds, users, Mac nodes, alerts, plans, backups, analytics\n- **Client panel** (violet theme) — build submission, certificate/profile management, webhooks, API tokens, team, billing, support\n- **Notification bell** — real-time dropdown with mark-as-read\n- **Profile dropdowns** — Change Password modal, Security modal (2FA + session management)\n- **Build log viewer** — animated streaming terminal with download IPA\n- **Charts** — all pure SVG, no dependencies (SvgBar, SvgGroupBar, SvgArea, SvgPie, Spark)\n- **Support chatbot** — keyword-based knowledge base with 14 topics\n- **Mobile** — responsive with slide-in sidebar overlay\n\n## Connect to backend\n\n```bash\n# Copy the integration helpers from the backend package\ncp ../macbuild-server/frontend-integration/api.js src/lib/api.js\ncp ../macbuild-server/frontend-integration/useSocket.js src/hooks/useSocket.js\n\n# Set API URL in .env\nVITE_API_URL=http://localhost:3001/api\n```', 4, 'tauri', '2026-05-25 00:43:19'),
