('50f0e1de-d653-48e7-8433-1534ecaf04a6', '81612d44-6768-4c94-a04e-def124844640', 'This commit represents a comprehensive refactoring of the entire frontend codebase, transforming a monolithic 11,254-line App.tsx file into a maintainable, scalable, and modern React application.\r\n\r\n## Major Changes:\r\n\r\n### Architecture & Structure\r\n- Created proper folder structure (components, pages, hooks, services, etc.)\r\n- Implemented clean component architecture with separation of concerns\r\n- Reduced main App.tsx from 11,254 lines to 13 lines\r\n- Backed up original App.tsx as App.tsx.backup for reference\r\n\r\n### Routing & Navigation\r\n- Installed and configured React Router DOM\r\n- Implemented protected routes with authentication guards\r\n- Created route-based navigation system\r\n- Added bottom navigation component\r\n\r\n### State Management\r\n- Created AuthContext for global authentication state\r\n- Implemented useAuth hook for easy auth state access\r\n- Set up proper context providers\r\n\r\n### TypeScript & Type Safety\r\n- Created comprehensive TypeScript types for all entities\r\n- Added proper type definitions (User, LikeLemba, Goal, Transaction, etc.)\r\n- Configured Vite environment types\r\n\r\n### Internationalization\r\n- Installed and configured react-i18next\r\n- Extracted all translations fr', 1, 'tauri', '2026-05-25 00:43:20'),
('50f227b5-1821-4822-80eb-294792dffa80', '30302ab6-38fa-49dc-8564-431709f610e4', 'My edited first READM', 0, 'tauri', '2026-05-25 00:43:19'),
('511c7342-62b3-4982-8d20-5d92210901d6', '399fd314-6581-4c4b-a300-01873157cce5', '# Tchopé 🇨🇲\n\nApplication mobile de recettes camerounaises. Découvrez, cuisinez et partagez les saveurs authentiques du Cameroun.\n\n## Fonctionnalités\n\n- **116+ recettes** camerounaises authentiques avec ingrédients et étapes détaillées\n- **Recherche avancée** par nom, ingrédient, durée, niveau de piment\n- **Filtres par région** (10 régions du Cameroun)\n- **Favoris** persistants (AsyncStorage)\n- **Cookbook personnel** — ajoutez vos propres recettes avec photo\n- **Timer de cuisson** avec bulle flottante et alerte à la fin\n- **Recettes en vidéo** — tutoriels YouTube intégrés pour 23+ plats\n- **Mode sombre** complet\n- **Bilingue** français / anglais (changement instantané)\n- **Partage de recettes** formatées (ingrédients + étapes)\n\n## Stack technique\n\n- **Expo SDK 54** (managed workflow)\n- **TypeScript**\n- **expo-router** v6 (file-based routing)\n- **NativeWind v5** (TailwindCSS pour React Native)\n- **expo-image** pour le chargement d\'images\n- **expo-image-picker** pour l\'ajout de photos\n- **AsyncStorage** pour la persistance locale\n- **expo-haptics** pour le retour haptique\n\n## Structure du projet', 0, 'tauri', '2026-05-25 00:43:19'),
('52f70ffb-965e-43a7-9fb3-07b1d8f9a35d', '81612d44-6768-4c94-a04e-def124844640', 'type definitions (User, LikeLemba, Goal, Transaction, etc.)\r\n- Configured Vite environment types\r\n\r\n### Internationalization\r\n- Installed and configured react-i18next\r\n- Extracted all translations from hardcoded strings\r\n- Created separate translation files (en.json, fr.json)\r\n- Implemented proper i18n configuration\r\n\r\n### API Layer\r\n- Created abstraction layer for all API calls\r\n- Implemented ApiClient with token management\r\n- Created service modules (auth, circles, goals, transactions)\r\n- Added proper error handling and TypeScript types\r\n- Implemented token storage and refresh logic\r\n\r\n### UI Components\r\n- Created reusable UI components (Button, Input, Card, Badge, Modal)\r\n- Built layout components (Header, BottomNavigation)\r\n- Implemented consistent styling with Tailwind CSS\r\n- Added proper TypeScript props and interfaces\r\n\r\n### Pages\r\n- Created page components (Home, Circles, Wallet, Card, Profile)\r\n- Implemented proper page structure with headers\r\n- Set up placeholder content for migration\r\n\r\n### Security\r\n- Comprehensive security review documented in SECURITY_REVIEW.md\r\n- Identified critical vulnerabilities in auth and payment flows\r\n- Documented recommendations for secure i', 2, 'tauri', '2026-05-25 00:43:20'),
('5365b50e-efb3-4f95-9510-8d712a71fe5f', '02e08f87-c902-4bfc-9435-efaa1833a929', 'Issue #2: Onsignal integration\nState: closed\nLabels: \n\n## Summary by Sourcery\n\nUpdate OneSignal configuration and add Android Google services config file.\n\nNew Features:\n- Add Android google-services.json configuration file for Firebase/Google services integration.\n\nEnhancements:\n- Update OneSignal application ID in the mobile app configuration.', 0, 'tauri', '2026-05-25 00:43:19'),
