('542e556f-6384-4eec-b192-77a4ca05cbad', '3afda09f-6fb0-4e22-a6ab-b1075a90f935', 'Issue #4: feat: Extract all screens from original App.tsx into separate page files\nState: closed\nLabels: \n\n- Created AppContext with all shared state (circles, goals, notifications, transactions, user info, support tickets, security logs, live chat, group chats)\r\n- Updated BottomNavigation to match original design with center elevated Join button\r\n- Updated routes with React Router tab sync and /goals route\r\n- Home.tsx: HomeScreen, NotificationsScreen, WhatsHotScreen\r\n- Circles.tsx: CirclesScreen, JoinScreen, and 21 sub-screens (all create/join flows, group chat, referral, likelemba details, payout methods)\r\n- Wallet.tsx: PaymentsScreen and 10 sub-screens (transaction history, financial dashboard, payment settings, saved cards)\r\n- Card.tsx: CardScreen with virtual card display, freeze/unfreeze, top-up flow, payment method management\r\n- Profile.tsx: ProfileScreen and 16 sub-screens (personal info, documents, security, support, live chat, FAQ)\r\n- Goals.tsx: MyGoalsScreen and 6 sub-screens (goal detail, create goal, saving programs, plan upgrade)\r\n- All original JSX layouts and designs preserved exactly as-is\r\n\r\nhttps://claude.ai/code/session_01DQYEizP5oC7ge3u6Uq7Tpu', 0, 'tauri', '2026-05-25 00:43:19'),
('55dd0b3e-5790-485c-93e7-9426bb8651f1', '2d86a639-860a-4270-b80b-ccc5cdce3716', 'If you can\'t get this to work, see the [Troubleshooting](https://reactnative.dev/docs/troubleshooting) page.\n\n# Learn More\n\nTo learn more about React Native, take a look at the following resources:\n\n\n\n- [React Native Website](https://reactnative.dev) - learn more about React Native.\n- [Getting Started](https://reactnative.dev/docs/environment-setup) - an **overview** of React Native and how setup your environment.\n- [Learn the Basics](https://reactnative.dev/docs/getting-started) - a **guided tour** of the React Native **basics**.\n- [Blog](https://reactnative.dev/blog) - read the latest official React Native **Blog** posts.\n- [`@facebook/react-native`](https://github.com/facebook/react-native) - the Open Source; GitHub **repository** for React Native.\n#\0 \0A\0p\0p\0_\0a\0n\0d\0r\0o\0i\0d\0\r\0', 3, 'tauri', '2026-05-25 00:43:19'),
('56f1af10-a580-4af9-97a2-cc0c923a8bde', '1e673316-5dbd-40d2-b95c-8f8e0433dd26', '.jsx  # Revenue/profit charts + build stats\n│   │\n│   └── client/\n│       ├── ClientSidebar.jsx   # Sidebar + plan usage bar + ClientProfileWidget\n│       ├── ClientDashboard.jsx # KPI cards, recent builds, notifications preview\n│       ├── ClientBuilds.jsx    # My builds table + log viewer\n│       ├── ClientNewBuild.jsx  # Submit new build form\n│       ├── ClientCerts.jsx     # Certificate management\n│       ├── ClientProfiles.jsx  # Provisioning profile management\n│       ├── ClientWebhooks.jsx  # Webhook configuration\n│       ├── ClientTokens.jsx    # API token management\n│       ├── ClientTeam.jsx      # Team members + invite\n│       ├── ClientBilling.jsx   # Invoices + payment method\n│       ├── ClientSettings.jsx  # Profile, 2FA, notification prefs, danger zone\n│       └── ClientChatbot.jsx   # Floating support chatbot with knowledge base\n```', 3, 'tauri', '2026-05-25 00:43:19'),
