('64a59dd5-45ba-4340-a0e5-4867c02a47f1', '8215339c-5f49-482b-a7fa-6c0f7f65d692', 'gn login and registration screens with new gradient headers and improved form layouts.\n- Add security logs filtering UI by activity type and time period, wired to a new security service placeholder.\n\n\n\nEnhancements:\n- Update routing and protected route behavior to support splash, onboarding, and a dedicated authenticated home path.\n- Improve referral navigation from profile to the circles referral screen.\n- Extend documentation to reflect completion of all remaining features and backend integrations.', 1, 'tauri', '2026-05-25 00:43:20'),
('64fd1a2e-1c6a-430a-bd77-c611053c2087', 'aa656288-06bd-4cfd-a37d-1bb7ef3df988', 'trols in assistant messages.\n- Enable textarea-based message input with auto-resize and Enter-to-send behavior.\n- Add mobile sidebar overlay behavior and improved sidebar toggling for small screens.\n\n\n\nEnhancements:\n- Refresh the global color palette, typography, and component styles for a more modern, compact UI across chat, sidebar, and auth pages.\n- Redesign the chat layout, message styling, and header actions to better support long-form conversations and code snippets.\n- Rebuild the auth page with a two-panel branding layout, improved form fields, and clearer call-to-action copy.\n- Update avatars and branding to use a consistent NovAI identity, including new SVG icons for the app and assistant.\n- Improve markdown rendering for tables and code blocks, including updated spacing and highlighting styles.\n\nChores:\n- Refine the Ollama connection error message to provide clearer startup instructions for users.', 1, 'tauri', '2026-05-25 00:43:20'),
('657a66c8-2a7d-405b-bedd-08e912c81e67', '97b0b299-4f9d-43c8-b7bb-c53028bac5b9', 'nfo:\n  - can_edu_id int NOT NULL\n  - can_id varchar NOT NULL\n  - degree_name varchar NOT NULL\n  - university_name varchar NOT NULL\n  - cgp varchar NOT NULL\n  - comments varchar\n  - sequencee varchar\n\n\n\nTABLE candidate_interview:\n  - can_int_id int NOT NULL\n  - can_id varchar NOT NULL\n  - job_adv_id varchar NOT NULL\n  - interview_date varchar NOT NULL\n  - interviewer_id varchar NOT NULL\n  - interview_marks varchar NOT NULL\n  - written_total_marks varchar NOT NULL\n  - mcq_total_marks varchar NOT NULL\n  - total_marks varchar NOT NULL\n  - recommandation varchar NOT NULL\n  - selection varchar NOT NULL\n  - details varchar NOT NULL\n\nTABLE candidate_selection:\n  - can_sel_id int NOT NULL\n  - can_id varchar NOT NULL\n  - employee_id varchar NOT NULL\n  - pos_id varchar NOT NULL\n  - selection_terms varchar\n\nTABLE candidate_shortlist:\n  - can_short_id int NOT NULL\n  - can_id varchar NOT NULL\n  - job_adv_id int NOT NULL\n  - date_of_shortlist varchar NOT NULL\n  - interview_date varchar NOT NULL', 5, 'tauri', '2026-05-25 00:43:20'),
('667c2b91-7c9e-4a4b-b700-cd612e0f5911', '1a01e3da-ab4b-44ee-b53e-d0dc55c66a6a', 'PR #1: Claude/review chatbot 1 i2q3\nState: closed\nLabels: \n\n## Summary by Sourcery\n\nIntroduce a full Flask-based web chatbot application powered by local Ollama models with persistent multi-conversation support and user accounts.\n\nNew Features:\n- Add a Flask web app that streams responses from a local Ollama model with conversation history and per-user context.\n- Implement user registration, login, and logout with password hashing and session-based authentication.\n- Provide multi-conversation management with titles, deletion, and export to text files per user.\n- Add a rich chat UI with sidebar conversation list, Markdown rendering, syntax-highlighted code blocks, and typing indicators.\n\nEnhancements:\n- Introduce a SQLite-backed persistence layer for users, conversations, and messages with helper access functions.\n\nBuild:\n- Add Python runtime dependencies for Flask, requests, and python-dotenv in requirements.txt.\n\nDocumentation:\n- Expand README with French setup, configuration, and usage instructions for running the local Ollama-powered chatbot.', 0, 'tauri', '2026-05-25 00:43:19'),
('672b4151-67ce-4db6-aa51-b15fecbe7344', '26f926f1-7b0f-408b-8a9c-ab835f670fbc', 'il) and export corresponding page components for app-wide use.\n- Define stub backend controllers for payments, goals, transactions, notifications, and referrals to scaffold future API functionality.\n\n\n\nEnhancements:\n- Extend the users table schema to include separate first/last names, phone, referral, plan tier, balances, and KYC-related fields.\n- Configure Laravel API routing and CORS middleware for the new API routes file and remove the legacy CORS config.\n- Implement a backend UserController with endpoints for profile retrieval, profile updates, password/passcode changes, and KYC document upload.\n- Align auth data contracts with backend expectations by switching to email-based login, adding password confirmation, and verifying email via user_id/OTP.\n\nDocumentation:\n- Add detailed integration status, test results, and implementation completion documentation to track frontend-backend integration, remaining work, and testing procedures.', 1, 'tauri', '2026-05-25 00:43:19'),
