('67f27f82-15c0-43fb-82ff-74f0c8318bf2', 'b6fd8155-16f3-4c3f-9a21-bd95a3e3125f', 'PR #8: Claude/review project m vnwt\nState: closed\nLabels: \n\n## Summary by Sourcery\n\nImplement full goal management API for authenticated users and adjust a wallet icon usage in the Circles page.\n\nNew Features:\n- Add CRUD, contribution, withdrawal, progress, and savings program enrollment endpoints for user goals in the API.\n\nEnhancements:\n- Expose predefined savings programs and computed goal metrics through the goals API.\n- Standardize wallet icon usage on the Circles page by switching to the shared WalletIcon component.', 0, 'tauri', '2026-05-25 00:43:20'),
('688e85f5-3558-47d9-a6a1-08ec832fdb4c', '5dd8fc37-3c86-4d1a-b7ab-4235c5585acd', 'NOT NULL\n\nTABLE purchase_return_details:\n  - preturn_id int NOT NULL\n  - product_id bigint NOT NULL\n  - qty int NOT NULL\n  - product_rate float NOT NULL\n  - store_id int NOT NULL\n  - discount float\n\n\n\nTABLE purchaseitem:\n  - purID int NOT NULL\n  - invoiceid varchar\n  - suplierID int NOT NULL\n  - paymenttype int\n  - bankid int\n  - total_price decimal NOT NULL\n  - paid_amount decimal\n  - details text\n  - purchasedate date NOT NULL\n  - purchaseexpiredate date NOT NULL\n  - savedby int NOT NULL\n\nTABLE qr_orders:\n  - id int NOT NULL\n  - order_code varchar NOT NULL\n  - customer_id int\n  - table_id int\n  - total_amount decimal NOT NULL\n  - payment_status enum\n  - order_status enum\n  - order_time datetime\n  - updated_at datetime\n\nTABLE qr_payments:\n  - payment_id int NOT NULL\n  - order_id int NOT NULL\n  - amount decimal NOT NULL\n  - method varchar\n  - transaction_id varchar\n  - payment_date datetime\n\nTABLE qr_tables:\n  - table_id int NOT NULL\n  - table_name varchar NOT NULL\n  - qr_code varchar\n  - status enum\n\nTABLE rate_type:\n  - id int NOT NULL\n  - r_type_name varchar NOT NULL', 25, 'tauri', '2026-05-25 00:43:19'),
('6a2c9b85-e1df-4bd0-932a-e36876c5670d', '7c5f2bda-769a-4b45-bda5-4fec14b88ec6', 'PR #7: Claude/review project m vnwt\nState: closed\nLabels:\n\n## Summary by Sourcery\n\nImplement final optional features and onboarding experience across circles, goals, wallet, auth, profile, and documentation to complete the app feature set.\n\nNew Features:\n- Add public circle discovery screen with search and the ability to join public circles from the backend.\n- Introduce payout slot selection backed by live slot data with fallback demo slots.\n- Add identity verification flow with national ID upload simulation before completing circle registration.\n- Implement splash and multi-step onboarding screens with persisted completion state and initial routing logic.\n- Provide edit modals for circles and savings goals to update key details via backend services.\n- Enable wallet balance display (card vs wallet) along with transaction filtering by type and date range, plus a payment confirmation modal for contributions.\n- Redesign login and registration screens with new gradient headers and improved form layouts.\n- Add security logs filtering UI by activity type and time period, wired to a new security service placeholder.', 0, 'tauri', '2026-05-25 00:43:20'),
('6accc21b-d530-489c-96b2-e98df0244925', '389e21f4-3ba9-4b80-b6b0-4ca20028693c', 'trols in assistant messages.\n- Enable textarea-based message input with auto-resize and Enter-to-send behavior.\n- Add mobile sidebar overlay behavior and improved sidebar toggling for small screens.\n\n\n\nEnhancements:\n- Refresh the global color palette, typography, and component styles for a more modern, compact UI across chat, sidebar, and auth pages.\n- Redesign the chat layout, message styling, and header actions to better support long-form conversations and code snippets.\n- Rebuild the auth page with a two-panel branding layout, improved form fields, and clearer call-to-action copy.\n- Update avatars and branding to use a consistent NovAI identity, including new SVG icons for the app and assistant.\n- Improve markdown rendering for tables and code blocks, including updated spacing and highlighting styles.\n\nChores:\n- Refine the Ollama connection error message to provide clearer startup instructions for users.', 1, 'tauri', '2026-05-25 00:43:19'),
('6b4fa265-6f4c-4001-871d-f9d2bd8f02e8', 'd1363221-c51b-4945-a58d-047800deed03', 'Welcome to Boostrap\nWe got tired of mistyping Bootstrap so we created Boostrap.com. Click Here for GetBootstrap.com. Or Click Here for other popular Bootstrap resources. Finally, need a simple html editor that works with Bootstrap? Bookmark this page.\nEnter Custom HTML <>\nSample Code Snippet:\nBootstrap · The most popular HTML, CSS, and JS library in the world.\nFree One Page HTML Code we created and based this site on\nBig Badass Bootstrap List\n300+ Useful Bootstrap Resources\nBootstrap Templates on WrapBootstrap\nBootstrap Themes at BootstrapZero\nBootstrapious.com\nWelcome to the Bootstrapious Resources section, a curated list of the tools and websites\nStart Bootstrap creates free, open source, MIT license, Bootstrap themes, templates, and code snippets\nDiscover thousands of easy to customize themes, templates & CMS products, made by world-class developers\nBootstrap Web Hosting\nOur favorite webhost Siteground\nBootstrap 5 code snippets', 0, 'tauri', '2026-05-25 00:43:20'),
