('7a90a637-32e2-4cc0-979f-fbf0bce0ae93', '8e978e50-7f54-4330-a22f-32ab9dcff751', 'Issue #5: Claude/review project m vnwt\nState: closed\nLabels: \n\n## Summary by Sourcery\n\nEnable real email delivery for OTP verification and expand frontend screens to consume additional app context for savings circles and LikeLemba flows.\n\nNew Features:\n- Send OTP verification codes via email using the configured mailer instead of only logging them.\n\nBug Fixes:\n- Wire the profile logout button directly to the authentication logout function.\n\nEnhancements:\n- Expose additional user and LikeLemba/circle fields from global app context to the Home, Wallet, Profile, and Goals screens for richer UI behavior.\n- Add support for finished circles and circle selection state in the wallet view.\n- Include active LikeLemba information in the goals page logic.', 0, 'tauri', '2026-05-25 00:43:20'),
('7bb2c0ec-565b-4865-a0a3-15483d8b79df', '97b0b299-4f9d-43c8-b7bb-c53028bac5b9', 'l\n\nTABLE tbl_token:\n  - tokenid int NOT NULL\n  - tokencode varchar NOT NULL\n  - tokenrate decimal NOT NULL\n  - tokenstartdate date NOT NULL\n  - tokenendate date NOT NULL\n  - tokenstatus int NOT NULL\n\n\n\nTABLE tbl_updateitems:\n  - updateid int NOT NULL\n  - ordid int NOT NULL\n  - menuid int NOT NULL\n  - qty decimal NOT NULL\n  - adonsqty varchar\n  - addonsid varchar\n  - varientid int NOT NULL\n  - addonsuid int\n  - isupdate varchar\n  - insertdate date\n\nTABLE tbl_version_checker:\n  - vid int NOT NULL\n  - version varchar\n  - disable int NOT NULL\n\nTABLE tbl_waiterappcart:\n  - weaterappid int NOT NULL\n  - waiterid int NOT NULL\n  - alladdOnsName varchar\n  - total_addonsprice decimal\n  - totaladdons int\n  - addons_name varchar\n  - addons_id int\n  - addons_price double\n  - addonsQty int\n  - component varchar\n  - destcription text\n  - itemnotes varchar\n  - offerIsavailable int\n  - offerstartdate date\n  - OffersRate int\n  - offerendate date\n  - price decimal\n  - ProductsID int NOT NULL\n  - ProductImage varchar NOT NULL\n  - ProductName varchar NOT NULL\n  - productvat int\n  - quantity int NOT NULL\n  - variantName varchar NOT NULL\n  - variantid int NOT NULL\n  - orderid int', 39, 'tauri', '2026-05-25 00:43:20'),
('7cd205ec-13d6-4b14-b98e-9cb6700416ac', 'bcfec2df-84a7-436e-b8ad-703080efe99a', 'PR #1: Claude/review chatbot 1 i2q3\nState: closed\nLabels: \n\n## Summary by Sourcery\n\nIntroduce a full Flask-based web chatbot application powered by local Ollama models with persistent multi-conversation support and user accounts.\n\nNew Features:\n- Add a Flask web app that streams responses from a local Ollama model with conversation history and per-user context.\n- Implement user registration, login, and logout with password hashing and session-based authentication.\n- Provide multi-conversation management with titles, deletion, and export to text files per user.\n- Add a rich chat UI with sidebar conversation list, Markdown rendering, syntax-highlighted code blocks, and typing indicators.\n\nEnhancements:\n- Introduce a SQLite-backed persistence layer for users, conversations, and messages with helper access functions.\n\nBuild:\n- Add Python runtime dependencies for Flask, requests, and python-dotenv in requirements.txt.\n\nDocumentation:\n- Expand README with French setup, configuration, and usage instructions for running the local Ollama-powered chatbot.', 0, 'tauri', '2026-05-25 00:43:20'),
('7cf59daf-234b-417d-9358-ed49f8d1a6d7', 'd7f25929-c07b-458f-bd4c-6f6a89fdc212', '/docs/advanced-configuration)\n\n### Deployment\n\nThis section has moved here: [https://facebook.github.io/create-react-app/docs/deployment](https://facebook.github.io/create-react-app/docs/deployment)\n\n\n\n### `npm run build` fails to minify\n\nThis section has moved here: [https://facebook.github.io/create-react-app/docs/troubleshooting#npm-run-build-fails-to-minify](https://facebook.github.io/create-react-app/docs/troubleshooting#npm-run-build-fails-to-minify', 3, 'tauri', '2026-05-25 00:43:20'),
('7cf666ab-0225-4fd6-a9e3-a018b8562029', 'bbf5c610-6214-4659-b0d6-5f2b9be91d63', 'd REFACTORING_GUIDE.md with complete migration guide\r\n- Documented new architecture and folder structure\r\n- Added examples and best practices\r\n- Created development workflow guidelines\r\n- Added .env.example for environment configuration\r\n\r\n### Testing & Build\r\n- Fixed TypeScript compilation errors\r\n- Successfully built production bundle\r\n- Verified all imports and dependencies\r\n\r\n## Files Added:\r\n- src/components/ui/* (Button, Input, Card, Badge, Modal)\r\n- src/components/layout/* (Header, BottomNavigation)\r\n- src/pages/* (Home, Circles, Wallet, Card, Profile)\r\n- src/context/AuthContext.tsx\r\n- src/services/* (api, auth, circles, goals, transactions)\r\n- src/types/index.ts\r\n- src/i18n/* (config, en.json, fr.json)\r\n- src/routes/index.tsx\r\n- src/vite-env.d.ts\r\n- SECURITY_REVIEW.md\r\n- REFACTORING_GUIDE.md\r\n- .env.example\r\n\r\n## Dependencies Added:\r\n- react-router-dom: ^6.x\r\n- react-i18next: ^14.x\r\n- i18next: ^23.x\r\n\r\n## Migration Status:\r\n✅ Core architecture complete\r\n✅ Type system established\r\n✅ API layer ready\r\n✅ Basic pages created\r\n🚧 Screen migration from old App.tsx in progress\r\n\r\n## Next Steps:\r\n- Migrate remaining screens from App.tsx.backup\r\n- Implement authentication flow\r\n- Add form validation\r\n- Implement error boundaries\r\n- Add loading states and notifications\r\n- Write tests\r\n\r\nhttps://claude.ai/code/session_01DQYEizP5oC7ge3u6Uq7Tpu', 2, 'tauri', '2026-05-25 00:43:20'),
