('7d410b0b-87cd-4535-abc5-a898a802af33', '0bf6869f-3785-43d7-9556-f10fcfc6fb2b', 'il) and export corresponding page components for app-wide use.\n- Define stub backend controllers for payments, goals, transactions, notifications, and referrals to scaffold future API functionality.\n\n\n\nEnhancements:\n- Extend the users table schema to include separate first/last names, phone, referral, plan tier, balances, and KYC-related fields.\n- Configure Laravel API routing and CORS middleware for the new API routes file and remove the legacy CORS config.\n- Implement a backend UserController with endpoints for profile retrieval, profile updates, password/passcode changes, and KYC document upload.\n- Align auth data contracts with backend expectations by switching to email-based login, adding password confirmation, and verifying email via user_id/OTP.\n\nDocumentation:\n- Add detailed integration status, test results, and implementation completion documentation to track frontend-backend integration, remaining work, and testing procedures.', 1, 'tauri', '2026-05-25 00:43:19'),
