('96529c67-4ed1-4933-8662-670dcca866cd', 'fac7f1c9-7727-4cb3-8294-d1c683894cf4', '# ChatBot IA\n\nUn chatbot web intelligent propulse par Ollama (modeles IA gratuits en local).\n\n## Prerequis\n\nInstallez Ollama sur votre machine :\n\n```bash\ncurl -fsSL https://ollama.ai/install.sh | sh\n```\n\nPuis telechargez un modele (Mistral par defaut) :\n\n```bash\nollama pull mistral\n```\n\n## Installation\n\n```bash\npip install -r requirements.txt\n```\n\n## Configuration (optionnel)\n\nCopiez le fichier `.env.example` en `.env` pour personnaliser :\n\n```bash\ncp .env.example .env\n```\n\nVariables disponibles :\n- `OLLAMA_BASE_URL` : URL d\'Ollama (defaut: `http://localhost:11434`)\n- `OLLAMA_MODEL` : Modele a utiliser (defaut: `mistral`)\n\nModeles recommandes : `mistral`, `llama3`, `gemma2`, `phi3`\n\n## Lancement\n\n1. Lancez Ollama :\n```bash\nollama serve\n```\n\n2. Lancez le chatbot :\n```bash\npython app.py\n```\n\n3. Ouvrez http://localhost:5000 dans votre navigateur.\n\n## Fonctionnalites\n\n- Inscription / connexion avec mot de passe securise\n- Multi-conversations avec barre laterale\n- Reponses en streaming (mot par mot)\n- Rendu Markdown avec coloration syntaxique du code\n- Export des conversations en fichier texte\n- Le bot se souvient de l\'utilisateur et de l\'historiqu', 0, 'tauri', '2026-05-25 00:43:20'),
('96741baa-11e3-45fe-b9f6-78acd84b82c4', 'cbb4429c-2b30-4fb4-bec7-8d7342f9b75d', 'migration\r\n\r\n### Security\r\n- Comprehensive security review documented in SECURITY_REVIEW.md\r\n- Identified critical vulnerabilities in auth and payment flows\r\n- Documented recommendations for secure implementation\r\n- Created security checklist for production readiness\r\n\r\n### Documentation\r\n- Created REFACTORING_GUIDE.md with complete migration guide\r\n- Documented new architecture and folder structure\r\n- Added examples and best practices\r\n- Created development workflow guidelines\r\n- Added .env.example for environment configuration\r\n\r\n### Testing & Build\r\n- Fixed TypeScript compilation errors\r\n- Successfully built production bundle\r\n- Verified all imports and dependencies\r\n\r\n## Files Added:\r\n- src/components/ui/* (Button, Input, Card, Badge, Modal)\r\n- src/components/layout/* (Header, BottomNavigation)\r\n- src/pages/* (Home, Circles, Wallet, Card, Profile)\r\n- src/context/AuthContext.tsx\r\n- src/services/* (api, auth, circles, goals, transactions)\r\n- src/types/index.ts\r\n- src/i18n/* (config, en.json, fr.json)\r\n- src/routes/index.tsx\r\n- src/vite-env.d.ts\r\n- SECURITY_REVIEW.md\r\n- REFACTORING_GUIDE.md\r\n- .env.example\r\n\r\n## Dependencies Added:\r\n- react-router-dom: ^6.x\r\n- react-i18next: ^14.x\r\n- i18next: ^23.x\r\n\r\n## Migration Status:\r\n✅ Core architecture complete\r\n✅ Type system established\r\n✅ API layer ready\r\n✅ Basic pages created\r\n🚧 Screen migration from old App.tsx in progress\r\n\r\n## Next Steps:\r\n- Migrate remaining screens from App.tsx.backup\r\n- Implement authentication flow\r\n- Add form validation\r\n- Implement error boundaries\r\n- Add loading states and notifications\r\n- Write tests\r\n\r\nhttps://claude.ai/code/session_01DQYEizP5oC7ge3u6Uq7Tpu', 3, 'tauri', '2026-05-25 00:43:20'),
