('9f3f7c8b-7a0b-4786-8731-35de1d44896c', 'bdd62ad3-5dd1-4e0f-a9cc-1b779adfacd9', 'Issue #2: Claude/review project m vnwt\nState: closed\nLabels:\n\n## Summary by Sourcery\n\nImplement end-to-end email-based authentication and verification flow across frontend and backend, expand user domain model, and document integration status and implementation progress.\n\nNew Features:\n- Add email-based registration, login, and verification flows on the frontend with dedicated Login, Register, and VerifyEmail pages wired into the router.\n- Introduce structured registration and verification response types and updated auth service methods to align with the new backend API contracts.\n- Expose new public auth routes (/login, /register, /verify-email) and export corresponding page components for app-wide use.\n- Define stub backend controllers for payments, goals, transactions, notifications, and referrals to scaffold future API functionality.', 0, 'tauri', '2026-05-25 00:43:20'),
('9f704c23-ba5c-458d-9255-d9c7a38de5a6', 'a8264584-a57b-4db4-af82-c5087a9efc57', 'Issue #7: Claude/review project m vnwt\nState: closed\nLabels: \n\n## Summary by Sourcery\n\nImplement final optional features and onboarding experience across circles, goals, wallet, auth, profile, and documentation to complete the app feature set.\n\nNew Features:\n- Add public circle discovery screen with search and the ability to join public circles from the backend.\n- Introduce payout slot selection backed by live slot data with fallback demo slots.\n- Add identity verification flow with national ID upload simulation before completing circle registration.\n- Implement splash and multi-step onboarding screens with persisted completion state and initial routing logic.\n- Provide edit modals for circles and savings goals to update key details via backend services.\n- Enable wallet balance display (card vs wallet) along with transaction filtering by type and date range, plus a payment confirmation modal for contributions.\n- Redesign login and registration screens with new gradient headers and improved form layouts.\n- Add security logs filtering UI by activity type and time period, wired to a new security service placeholder.\n\nEnhancements:\n- Update routing and protected route behavior to support splash, onboarding, and a dedicated authenticated home path.\n- Improve referral navigation from profile to the circles referral screen.\n- Extend documentation to reflect completion of all remaining features and backend integrations.', 0, 'tauri', '2026-05-25 00:43:20'),
