('a26a93d0-3d09-48ee-9a29-16200c9afa88', '5dd8fc37-3c86-4d1a-b7ab-4235c5585acd', 'OT NULL\n  - Amount decimal NOT NULL\n\nTABLE acc_glsummarybalance:\n  - ID int NOT NULL\n  - COAID varchar\n  - Debit decimal\n  - Credit decimal\n  - FYear int\n  - CreateBy varchar\n  - CreateDate datetime\n\n\n\nTABLE acc_income_expence:\n  - ID int NOT NULL\n  - VNo varchar NOT NULL\n  - Student_Id varchar NOT NULL\n  - Date date NOT NULL\n  - Paymode varchar NOT NULL\n  - Perpose varchar NOT NULL\n  - Narration text NOT NULL\n  - StoreID int NOT NULL\n  - COAID varchar NOT NULL\n  - Amount decimal NOT NULL\n  - IsApprove tinyint NOT NULL\n  - CreateBy varchar NOT NULL\n  - CreateDate datetime NOT NULL\n\nTABLE acc_temp:\n  - COAID varchar NOT NULL\n  - Name varchar NOT NULL\n  - Debit decimal NOT NULL\n  - Credit decimal NOT NULL\n\nTABLE acc_transaction:\n  - ID int NOT NULL\n  - VNo varchar\n  - Vtype varchar\n  - VDate date\n  - COAID varchar NOT NULL\n  - Narration text\n  - Debit decimal\n  - Credit decimal\n  - StoreID int NOT NULL\n  - IsPosted char\n  - CreateBy varchar\n  - CreateDate datetime\n  - UpdateBy varchar\n  - UpdateDate datetime\n  - IsAppove char', 1, 'tauri', '2026-05-25 00:43:19'),
('a2b0e864-5422-461a-8ce6-4e09cb6f420a', '207d596f-8788-4112-8111-6aec09070d30', 'ops...\n    ├── driver/   (15) → Dashboard, Delivery, Navigation, Wallet, Zones...\n    └── common/   (5)  → Settings, Help, About, Terms, Privacy\n```\n\n## 🔌 Guide intégration API\n\nChaque fichier `src/data/*.js` → remplacer par appel API :\n\n| Mock file | API endpoint | Méthodes |\n|---|---|---|\n| products.js | `/api/products` | GET POST PUT DELETE |\n| vendors.js | `/api/vendors` | GET |\n| categories.js | `/api/categories` | GET |\n| reviews.js | `/api/products/:id/reviews` | GET POST |\n| vendorData.js | `/api/vendor/*` | GET POST PUT |\n| driverData.js | `/api/driver/*` | GET POST PUT |\n\n### Pattern API recommandé\n```jsx\n// Créer: src/services/api.js\nimport axios from \'axios\';\nexport const api = axios.create({ baseURL: \'https://api.lamuka.cg\' });\n\n// Dans un écran:\nimport { api } from \"../../services/api\";\nconst [products, setProducts] = useState([]);\nuseEffect(() => { api.get(\'/products\').then(r => setProducts(r.data)) }, []);\n```\n\n### Services à créer dans `src/services/`\n- `api.js` — Instance Axios de base\n- `authService.js` — Phone+OTP, Social login\n- `productService.js` — CRUD articles\n- `orderService.js` — Commandes\n- `paymentService.js` — Airtel Money, MTN MoMo, Kolo Pay\n- `chatService.js` — WebSocket temps réel\n\n## 📞 Contact\n**Joeldy Tsina** — Lamuka Tech | 📱 +242 064 663 469 | ✉️ joeldytsina94@gmail.com\n\n© 2026 Lamuka Tech', 1, 'tauri', '2026-05-25 00:43:19'),
('a2cfd4c1-11e5-4c6f-bdef-0b1ca620c39a', '0b911ef2-3024-46de-ac69-bdd2cfb8c9a4', '→ Tab bar (4 onglets)\n    index.tsx              → Accueil\n    search.tsx             → Recherche\n    cookbook.tsx            → Mon Cookbook\n    settings.tsx           → Paramètres\n  recipe/[id].tsx          → Détail recette\n  add-recipe.tsx           → Ajouter une recette\n  recipe-videos.tsx        → Vidéos YouTube\n  recipes-list.tsx         → Liste filtrée (région / toutes)\ncomponents/                → Composants réutilisables\nconstants/\n  translations.ts          → i18n FR/EN\n  images.ts                → Mapping images (Wikimedia Commons)\n  videos.ts                → Mapping vidéos YouTube\ncontext/\n  SettingsContext.tsx       → Thème + langue\n  TimerContext.tsx          → Timer de cuisson flottant\n  ToastContext.tsx          → Toasts visuels\ndata/\n  recipes.ts               → 116 recettes parsées\nhooks/                     → Hooks personnalisés\ntypes/                     → Types TypeScript\n```\n\n## Lancer en développement\n\n```bash\n# Installer les dépendances\nnpm install\n\n# Lancer le serveur de développement\nnpx expo start\n\n# Scanner le QR code avec Expo Go (iOS/Android)\n```\n\n## Build pour les stores\n\n### Prérequis\n\n1. Installer EAS CLI :\n```bash\nnpm install -g eas-cli\n```\n\n2. Se connecter à son compte Expo :\n```bash\neas login\n```\n\n3. Configurer le projet (une seule fois) :\n```bash\neas build:configure\n```\n\n### Build iOS (App Store)\n\n```bash\n# Build de production pour iOS\neas build --platform ios --profile production\n\n# Soumettre sur l\'App Store\neas submit --platf', 1, 'tauri', '2026-05-25 00:43:19'),
('a306899b-09c4-442f-bfa2-8e1ea24d2e4f', '389e21f4-3ba9-4b80-b6b0-4ca20028693c', 'Issue #2: Claude/review chatbot 1 i2q3\nState: closed\nLabels:\n\n## Summary by Sourcery\n\nRevamp the NovAI chat and auth interfaces with a new visual design and UX improvements, including enhanced message rendering and onboarding.\n\nNew Features:\n- Add quick-start suggestion cards on the welcome screen that prefill and submit example prompts.\n- Introduce code block headers with language labels and copy-to-clipboard controls in assistant messages.\n- Enable textarea-based message input with auto-resize and Enter-to-send behavior.\n- Add mobile sidebar overlay behavior and improved sidebar toggling for small screens.', 0, 'tauri', '2026-05-25 00:43:19'),
