('aa227342-64d6-4912-9127-f93b6a377cd7', '2b369c89-42d2-4511-a5cf-2ff50e39751d', 'Issue #1: Claude/review chatbot 1 i2q3\nState: closed\nLabels: \n\n## Summary by Sourcery\n\nIntroduce a full Flask-based web chatbot application powered by local Ollama models with persistent multi-conversation support and user accounts.\n\nNew Features:\n- Add a Flask web app that streams responses from a local Ollama model with conversation history and per-user context.\n- Implement user registration, login, and logout with password hashing and session-based authentication.\n- Provide multi-conversation management with titles, deletion, and export to text files per user.\n- Add a rich chat UI with sidebar conversation list, Markdown rendering, syntax-highlighted code blocks, and typing indicators.\n\nEnhancements:\n- Introduce a SQLite-backed persistence layer for users, conversations, and messages with helper access functions.\n\nBuild:\n- Add Python runtime dependencies for Flask, requests, and python-dotenv in requirements.txt.\n\nDocumentation:\n- Expand README with French setup, configuration, and usage instructions for running the local Ollama-powered chatbot.', 0, 'tauri', '2026-05-25 00:43:19'),
