('bbc4d371-6222-4b25-a3a6-bef51b9cb3a8', '6b69da2e-7fde-4afd-bb57-74bf4872d5d0', 'PR #6: Claude/review project m vnwt\nState: closed\nLabels:\n\n## Summary by Sourcery\n\nIntegrate the frontend with new and existing backend APIs for circles, goals, cards, notifications, payments, and support, replacing demo data and local-only state updates with persisted server-driven data flows.\n\nNew Features:\n- Add backend-powered circle chat, membership management, and join/create flows that load and persist data via circlesService.\n- Introduce goal contribution, withdrawal, and deletion capabilities wired to backend goalsService with a reusable contribution modal.\n- Implement virtual card top-up and freeze/unfreeze actions backed by cardService with real balance retrieval.\n- Add full CRUD support for payment methods using a dedicated paymentMethodsService.\n- Introduce paymentsService and supportService to handle contributions and support tickets via backend APIs.\n- Add notificationsService to synchronize notification read state with the server and fetch real notifications.\n- Expose global loading, error, and refreshData handling in AppContext tied to authenticated user data fetching.', 0, 'tauri', '2026-05-25 00:43:19'),
('bc2cd53d-bbad-4bf3-9725-be902819822d', '26f926f1-7b0f-408b-8a9c-ab835f670fbc', 'PR #2: Claude/review project m vnwt\nState: closed\nLabels:\n\n## Summary by Sourcery\n\nImplement end-to-end email-based authentication and verification flow across frontend and backend, expand user domain model, and document integration status and implementation progress.\n\nNew Features:\n- Add email-based registration, login, and verification flows on the frontend with dedicated Login, Register, and VerifyEmail pages wired into the router.\n- Introduce structured registration and verification response types and updated auth service methods to align with the new backend API contracts.\n- Expose new public auth routes (/login, /register, /verify-email) and export corresponding page components for app-wide use.\n- Define stub backend controllers for payments, goals, transactions, notifications, and referrals to scaffold future API functionality.', 0, 'tauri', '2026-05-25 00:43:19'),
