('be8319bb-9311-4e67-91d0-c89ea77e2a05', '1e673316-5dbd-40d2-b95c-8f8e0433dd26', '# Mac Build Cloud — Frontend\n\niOS CI/CD SaaS platform dashboard. Built with **React 18 + Vite + Tailwind CSS**.\n\n## Stack\n\n| Tool | Version | Role |\n|---|---|---|\n| React | 18 | UI framework |\n| Vite | 5 | Dev server + bundler |\n| Tailwind CSS | 3 | Utility-first styling |\n| Pure SVG | — | Charts (no external lib) |\n\n## Setup\n\n```bash\nnpm install\nnpm run dev       # http://localhost:5173\nnpm run build     # production build → dist/\nnpm run preview   # preview production build\n```\n\n## Demo credentials\n\n| Role | Email | Password |\n|---|---|---|\n| Admin | admin@macbuild.cloud | password |\n| Client | alex@company.io | password |\n\n## Project structure', 0, 'tauri', '2026-05-25 00:43:19'),
