('c0783cb5-5987-4fa5-8715-47dd9cbcdc1b', '7264e196-8418-4771-a47e-91cb04f7bda8', 'Issue #7: Claude/review project m vnwt\nState: closed\nLabels:\n\n## Summary by Sourcery\n\nImplement final optional features and onboarding experience across circles, goals, wallet, auth, profile, and documentation to complete the app feature set.\n\nNew Features:\n- Add public circle discovery screen with search and the ability to join public circles from the backend.\n- Introduce payout slot selection backed by live slot data with fallback demo slots.\n- Add identity verification flow with national ID upload simulation before completing circle registration.\n- Implement splash and multi-step onboarding screens with persisted completion state and initial routing logic.\n- Provide edit modals for circles and savings goals to update key details via backend services.\n- Enable wallet balance display (card vs wallet) along with transaction filtering by type and date range, plus a payment confirmation modal for contributions.\n- Redesign login and registration screens with new gradient headers and improved form layouts.\n- Add security logs filtering UI by activity type and time period, wired to a new security service placeholder.', 0, 'tauri', '2026-05-25 00:43:19'),
('c180a027-caf0-49fc-8607-485a76095429', 'd1b502be-04c6-48c9-a937-92a5d74647c5', 'trols in assistant messages.\n- Enable textarea-based message input with auto-resize and Enter-to-send behavior.\n- Add mobile sidebar overlay behavior and improved sidebar toggling for small screens.\n\n\n\nEnhancements:\n- Refresh the global color palette, typography, and component styles for a more modern, compact UI across chat, sidebar, and auth pages.\n- Redesign the chat layout, message styling, and header actions to better support long-form conversations and code snippets.\n- Rebuild the auth page with a two-panel branding layout, improved form fields, and clearer call-to-action copy.\n- Update avatars and branding to use a consistent NovAI identity, including new SVG icons for the app and assistant.\n- Improve markdown rendering for tables and code blocks, including updated spacing and highlighting styles.\n\nChores:\n- Refine the Ollama connection error message to provide clearer startup instructions for users.', 1, 'tauri', '2026-05-25 00:43:20'),
