('c5ddab4a-1792-4373-8707-23518e415f71', 'a8696a42-19ac-4dba-b8b4-af6fe90169cc', 'PR #2: Onsignal integration\nState: closed\nLabels: \n\n## Summary by Sourcery\n\nUpdate OneSignal configuration and add Android Google services config file.\n\nNew Features:\n- Add Android google-services.json configuration file for Firebase/Google services integration.\n\nEnhancements:\n- Update OneSignal application ID in the mobile app configuration.', 0, 'tauri', '2026-05-25 00:43:20'),
