('c97916f9-51de-40c9-876d-a8772415c0d6', 'e7045e85-d158-48d0-bb8e-3c467801c051', 'Issue #1: Firebase cloud messaging integration\nState: closed\nLabels: \n\n## Summary by Sourcery\n\nSwitch customer booking push notifications from OneSignal to Firebase Cloud Messaging and tidy related controller code.\n\nNew Features:\n- Send booking confirmation push notifications to customers via Firebase Cloud Messaging.\n\nEnhancements:\n- Simplify and reformat reservation booking controller logic and notification payload construction for readability.', 0, 'tauri', '2026-05-25 00:43:20'),
('c99e4d3a-f2c5-4ee4-aebc-cffed16cf872', '9939fcca-d385-4abf-be5b-0b65f8385c8f', 'PR #5: Claude/review project m vnwt\nState: closed\nLabels: \n\n## Summary by Sourcery\n\nEnable real email delivery for OTP verification and expand frontend screens to consume additional app context for savings circles and LikeLemba flows.\n\nNew Features:\n- Send OTP verification codes via email using the configured mailer instead of only logging them.\n\nBug Fixes:\n- Wire the profile logout button directly to the authentication logout function.\n\nEnhancements:\n- Expose additional user and LikeLemba/circle fields from global app context to the Home, Wallet, Profile, and Goals screens for richer UI behavior.\n- Add support for finished circles and circle selection state in the wallet view.\n- Include active LikeLemba information in the goals page logic.', 0, 'tauri', '2026-05-25 00:43:20'),
