('f59c2402-a0a5-44db-8f16-fd98facc4c78', 'd0af8ff8-3026-4367-bdf7-97b039517b24', 'gn login and registration screens with new gradient headers and improved form layouts.\n- Add security logs filtering UI by activity type and time period, wired to a new security service placeholder.\n\n\n\nEnhancements:\n- Update routing and protected route behavior to support splash, onboarding, and a dedicated authenticated home path.\n- Improve referral navigation from profile to the circles referral screen.\n- Extend documentation to reflect completion of all remaining features and backend integrations.', 1, 'tauri', '2026-05-25 00:43:20'),
('f5a7834d-1964-4c0e-a989-8178bbdc3b88', 'f11b15fc-01ea-48b4-8c5c-3bd600def225', 'Issue #5: Claude/review project m vnwt\nState: closed\nLabels: \n\n## Summary by Sourcery\n\nEnable real email delivery for OTP verification and expand frontend screens to consume additional app context for savings circles and LikeLemba flows.\n\nNew Features:\n- Send OTP verification codes via email using the configured mailer instead of only logging them.\n\nBug Fixes:\n- Wire the profile logout button directly to the authentication logout function.\n\nEnhancements:\n- Expose additional user and LikeLemba/circle fields from global app context to the Home, Wallet, Profile, and Goals screens for richer UI behavior.\n- Add support for finished circles and circle selection state in the wallet view.\n- Include active LikeLemba information in the goals page logic.', 0, 'tauri', '2026-05-25 00:43:20'),
