('f9f27ece-6933-4120-8a51-31209bfcd05e', '8215339c-5f49-482b-a7fa-6c0f7f65d692', 'PR #7: Claude/review project m vnwt\nState: closed\nLabels:\n\n## Summary by Sourcery\n\nImplement final optional features and onboarding experience across circles, goals, wallet, auth, profile, and documentation to complete the app feature set.\n\nNew Features:\n- Add public circle discovery screen with search and the ability to join public circles from the backend.\n- Introduce payout slot selection backed by live slot data with fallback demo slots.\n- Add identity verification flow with national ID upload simulation before completing circle registration.\n- Implement splash and multi-step onboarding screens with persisted completion state and initial routing logic.\n- Provide edit modals for circles and savings goals to update key details via backend services.\n- Enable wallet balance display (card vs wallet) along with transaction filtering by type and date range, plus a payment confirmation modal for contributions.\n- Redesign login and registration screens with new gradient headers and improved form layouts.\n- Add security logs filtering UI by activity type and time period, wired to a new security service placeholder.', 0, 'tauri', '2026-05-25 00:43:20'),
('fa9fd68e-b8ab-48d7-8cbe-437af294543f', '15c81855-2d8a-43a7-85f5-e373a7550619', 'to synchronize notification read state with the server and fetch real notifications.\n- Expose global loading, error, and refreshData handling in AppContext tied to authenticated user data fetching.\n\n\n\nEnhancements:\n- Replace seeded demo data in AppContext with real backend-driven initialization for circles, goals, transactions, notifications, and support tickets.\n- Update Home, Circles, Goals, Card, and Profile screens to consume backend data, improve error handling, and remove hardcoded copy in some profile sections.\n\nDocumentation:\n- Add BACKEND_INTEGRATION_STATUS and MISSING_FEATURES docs summarizing current backend integration coverage and remaining low-priority items.', 1, 'tauri', '2026-05-25 00:43:19'),
